00:48:42,111 --> 00:48:57,773
Bratteolas trabibus sublevit, ut omnis aurulenta
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Lux esset intus, ceu jubar sub ortu,
Subdidit et parias fulvis laquearibus columnas,
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Distinguit illic quas quaternus ordo. Tum camuros hyalo insigni varie cucurrit arcus.

248
00:48:57,773 --> 00:49:09,566
